App Engine code for LOL stats.

Use this command to deploy.
./appcfg.py -A lol-stats-test update lol_stats

From cloud console:
cd src/lol-stats-test/master
git pull --rebase origin
appcfg.py -A lol-stats-test update .


Riot API call examples,

Seed (1 time):
 Find players from featured.
  https://kr.api.pvp.net/observer-mode/rest/featured?api_key=7ff24dff-48c7-4df8-883b-d08d4787fefc
  https://kr.api.pvp.net/api/lol/kr/v1.4/summoner/by-name/c1ash?api_key=7ff24dff-48c7-4df8-883b-d08d4787fefc

Find matches:
 Scan players, find matches, "least recent updated summoner first".
 Note, matchhistory has detailed info, while matchlist has more matches.
  https://kr.api.pvp.net/api/lol/kr/v2.2/matchlist/by-summoner/30202240?api_key=7ff24dff-48c7-4df8-883b-d08d4787fefc

Update stats from matches (also players):
 Note, lane info is in the data.
  https://kr.api.pvp.net/api/lol/kr/v2.2/match/1995207724?api_key=7ff24dff-48c7-4df8-883b-d08d4787fefc


Find tier info:
  https://kr.api.pvp.net/api/lol/kr/v2.5/league/by-summoner/2077233/entry?api_key=7ff24dff-48c7-4df8-883b-d08d4787fefc

Only 500 calls are allowed in 10 minutes.
